  "response": "Here\u2019s a cool and catchy name idea for your new mobile shop in Telangana:\n\n**\"Telangana Mobilia\"**  \n- **\"Mobilia\"** combines \"mobile\" with a sleek, modern twist, while also hinting at mobility and convenience.  \n- It\u2019s easy to remember and has a local connection with \"Telangana\" in the name, making it relatable to your target audience.  \n\nOther suggestions:  \n1. **\"Gadget Galaxy Telangana\"**  \n2. **\"Mobile Mania Hub\"**  \n3. **\"HyTech Mobiles\"**  \n4. **\"The Mobile Bazaar\"**  \n5. **\"Connect Telangana\"**  \n6. **\"Smart Cell Zone\"**  \n7. **\"Telangana Tech Mart\"**  \n8. **\"Mobile Verse Telangana\"**  \n9. **\"Phone Planet Telangana\"**  \n10. **\"GadgetNest Telangana\"**\n\nMake sure the name aligns with your shop's vibe and services! Good luck with your new venture! \ud83d\ude80\ud83d\udcf1",
